  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TaC7">
<l>naḷirmatic caṭaiyaṉum nāṉmukak kaṭavuḷum</l>
<l>taḷiroḷi yimaiyavar talaivaṉu mutalā</l>
<l>yāvakai yulakamum yāvaru makappaṭa</l>
<l>nilanīr tīkāl cuṭariru vicumpu</l>
<l>malarcuṭar piṟavum ciṟituṭaṉ mayaṅka</l>
<l>voruporuṭ puṟappā ṭiṉṟi muḻuvatu</l>
<l>makappaṭak karantō rālilaic cērntavem</l>
<l>perumā māyaṉai yalla</l>
<l>torumā teyvamaṟ ṟuṭaiyamō yāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Apart from our lord, the Dark/Tricky one</l>
<l>who, while he took inside everybody and every kind of world</l>
<l>beginning with [that of] the one with matted locks [wearing] the cool moon, the god</l>
<l>with four faces and the leader of the unblinking ones, of sprouting brightness,</l>
<l>so that earth, water, fire, wind, the glowing vast sky,</l>
<l>and the blooming [celestial] lights and others were a little mixed up together,</l>
<l>without a single object occurring outside, hid</l>
<l>everything, so as to be inside, [and] lay down on one fig leaf,</l>
<l>– do we possess any other great god?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
